'''蛋白酶'''（{{lang-en|protease}}，proteinase）或'''肽酶'''（peptidase）是[[生物體|生物體]]內的一類[[酶|酶]]（酵素），它們能夠分解[[蛋白質|蛋白質]]。分解方法是打斷那些將[[氨基酸|氨基酸]]連結成多肽鏈的[[肽鍵|肽鍵]]。

蛋白酶是重要的[[工業|工業]]酶，佔全球總酶銷售量約六成，其中七成用於工業用途的蛋白酶用於食品[[發酵|發酵]]等方面<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Sabotič |first1=J |last2=Kos |first2=J |title=Microbial and fungal protease inhibitors--current and potential applications. |journal=Applied microbiology and biotechnology |date=2012-02 |volume=93 |issue=4 |pages=1351-75 |doi=10.1007/s00253-011-3834-x |pmid=22218770 |url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/m/pubmed/22218770/ |accessdate=2019-12-13 |archive-date=2020-03-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200315203124/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/m/pubmed/22218770/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，例如[[酸性|酸性]]蛋白酶用於[[傳統|傳統]]發酵食品和調味品的生產<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Lee |first1=YH |last2=Tominaga |first2=M |last3=Hayashi |first3=R |last4=Sakamoto |first4=K |last5=Yamada |first5=O |last6=Akita |first6=O |title=Aspergillus oryzae strains with a large deletion of the aflatoxin biosynthetic homologous gene cluster differentiated by chromosomal breakage. |journal=Applied microbiology and biotechnology |date=2006-09 |volume=72 |issue=2 |pages=339-45 |doi=10.1007/s00253-005-0282-5 |pmid=16673111 |url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/m/pubmed/16673111/ |accessdate=2019-12-13 |archive-date=2020-03-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200315203129/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/m/pubmed/16673111/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=te Biesebeke |first1=R |last2=Record |first2=E |last3=van Biezen |first3=N |last4=Heerikhuisen |first4=M |last5=Franken |first5=A |last6=Punt |first6=PJ |last7=van den Hondel |first7=CA |title=Branching mutants of Aspergillus oryzae with improved amylase and protease production on solid substrates. |journal=Applied microbiology and biotechnology |date=2005-11 |volume=69 |issue=1 |pages=44-50 |doi=10.1007/s00253-005-1968-4 |pmid=15909137 |url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/m/pubmed/15909137/ |accessdate=2019-12-13 |archive-date=2020-03-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200315203134/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/m/pubmed/15909137/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>及[[催化|催化]][[酪蛋白|酪蛋白]]沈澱；[[中性|中性]]蛋白酶因能夠去除[[水解|水解]]產物的[[苦_(味覺)|苦味]]而令[[醬油|醬油]]脫苦<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Machida |first1=M |last2=Asai |first2=K |last3=Sano |first3=M |last4=Tanaka |first4=T |last5=Kumagai |first5=T |last6=Terai |first6=G |last7=Kusumoto |first7=K |last8=Arima |first8=T |last9=Akita |first9=O |last10=Kashiwagi |first10=Y |last11=Abe |first11=K |last12=Gomi |first12=K |last13=Horiuchi |first13=H |last14=Kitamoto |first14=K |last15=Kobayashi |first15=T |last16=Takeuchi |first16=M |last17=Denning |first17=DW |last18=Galagan |first18=JE |last19=Nierman |first19=WC |last20=Yu |first20=J |last21=Archer |first21=DB |last22=Bennett |first22=JW |last23=Bhatnagar |first23=D |last24=Cleveland |first24=TE |last25=Fedorova |first25=ND |last26=Gotoh |first26=O |last27=Horikawa |first27=H |last28=Hosoyama |first28=A |last29=Ichinomiya |first29=M |last30=Igarashi |first30=R |last31=Iwashita |first31=K |last32=Juvvadi |first32=PR |last33=Kato |first33=M |last34=Kato |first34=Y |last35=Kin |first35=T |last36=Kokubun |first36=A |last37=Maeda |first37=H |last38=Maeyama |first38=N |last39=Maruyama |first39=J |last40=Nagasaki |first40=H |last41=Nakajima |first41=T |last42=Oda |first42=K |last43=Okada |first43=K |last44=Paulsen |first44=I |last45=Sakamoto |first45=K |last46=Sawano |first46=T |last47=Takahashi |first47=M |last48=Takase |first48=K |last49=Terabayashi |first49=Y |last50=Wortman |first50=JR |last51=Yamada |first51=O |last52=Yamagata |first52=Y |last53=Anazawa |first53=H |last54=Hata |first54=Y |last55=Koide |first55=Y |last56=Komori |first56=T |last57=Koyama |first57=Y |last58=Minetoki |first58=T |last59=Suharnan |first59=S |last60=Tanaka |first60=A |last61=Isono |first61=K |last62=Kuhara |first62=S |last63=Ogasawara |first63=N |last64=Kikuchi |first64=H |title=Genome sequencing and analysis of Aspergillus oryzae. |journal=Nature |date=2005-12-22 |volume=438 |issue=7071 |pages=1157-61 |doi=10.1038/nature04300 |pmid=16372010 |url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/m/pubmed/16372010/ |accessdate=2019-12-13 |archive-date=2020-03-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200315203140/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/m/pubmed/16372010/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>；[[鹼性|鹼性]]蛋白酶應用於食品[[烘烤|烘烤]]等方面<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Okuda |first1=M |last2=Sumitomo |first2=N |last3=Takimura |first3=Y |last4=Ogawa |first4=A |last5=Saeki |first5=K |last6=Kawai |first6=S |last7=Kobayashi |first7=T |last8=Ito |first8=S |title=A new subtilisin family: nucleotide and deduced amino acid sequences of new high-molecular-mass alkaline proteases from Bacillus spp. |journal=Extremophiles : life under extreme conditions |date=2004-06 |volume=8 |issue=3 |pages=229-35 |doi=10.1007/s00792-004-0381-8 |pmid=15022105 |url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/m/pubmed/15022105/ |accessdate=2019-12-13 |archive-date=2020-03-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200315203144/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/m/pubmed/15022105/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，因為能夠有效提高[[生麵團|生麵團]]的延性和韌性，並且增強[[麵包|麵包]]的起泡性。

== 分類 ==
目前已知的蛋白酶可以分成以下六大類：
* [[絲氨酸蛋白酶|絲氨酸蛋白酶]]（Serine proteases） 
* [[苏氨酸蛋白酶|苏氨酸蛋白酶]]（Threonine proteases） 
* [[半胱氨酸蛋白酶|半胱氨酸蛋白酶]]（Cysteine proteases） 
* [[天冬氨酸蛋白酶|天冬氨酸蛋白酶]]（Aspartic acid proteases）
* [[金屬蛋白酶|金屬蛋白酶]]（Metalloproteases） 
* [[谷氨酸蛋白酶|谷氨酸蛋白酶]]（Glutamic acid proteases）

